{"tid":669304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：曾被控85次 澳門黑的照鎖車門劏客","createTime":"2018-05-18T10:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T04:35:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf77e47073d82953416f06780f34da1a7117f7f","tid":669304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T10:40:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180518/20394383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F20394383&d=luYS1DMMKVOgiYg3u0Nvg10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a8c0f746\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F20394383&h=d04ff794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180518/20394383</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月18日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：曾被控85次<br />\n澳門黑的照鎖車門劏客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180518/large/a1506a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180518%2Flarge%2Fa1506a.gif&h=2908ba41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有台灣遊客喺fb話，遊澳門期間遇上的士司機濫收車資兼鎖門威嚇。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「澳門就是與別不同」，呢句澳門旅遊局推廣口號真係冇講錯。話說有位台灣遊客喺fb訴苦，話14號喺澳門搭的士去威尼斯人，睇錶21蚊，但司機坐地起價要收$100，仲鎖車門載遊客返原址，結果遊客太驚下話肯畀$50，司機就喺半路中途放低佢。遊客其後報警，警方拉咗司機，但有網民話原來司機已經放番。<br />\n<br />\n澳門警方翻查紀錄發現，涉案司機前年8月開始，試過被檢控85宗的士違規，包括濫收車資、拒載等，而違規期間揸過不同的士。<br />\n<br />\n唔少澳門網民已經對呢啲事見怪不怪，不過就好奇怪，點解俾人拉足85次仲可以繼續揸的士，反而曾經喺遊行期間於澳門特首官邸掟紙飛機嘅蘇嘉豪，就俾建制派聯手褫奪議席之餘，仲被正式起訴。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：車cam還原　泥頭車撼九巴<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點‧即聽"},{"pid":"d6c8d3fcdcaa524ee2e7f3b5afcac867b3163fe4","tid":669304,"uid":45368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"天下dc9一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8854fae5e4d34b3d8dbee06b50cb7328f90fd4","tid":669304,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6c8d3fcdcaa524ee2e7f3b5afcac867b3163fe4","tid":669304,"uid":45368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"天下dc9一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"澳門黑10倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港就過海，澳門就過橋"},{"pid":"c88b9480436135946a2181656dfcd4810d6207d0","tid":669304,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"澳門同大陸一撚樣講人事關系唔係講法律既，豬識條撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ac3f29f89c795cf69a438caffab70375d2e654","tid":669304,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"咁撚串，想問吓澳門警察廢唔廢<br />\n遇到咁報警有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c86ff9a3d3a38281ddf66f093e360880a4586d7","tid":669304,"uid":61271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"澳門的士都on撚9<br />\n喺街永遠截唔到<br />\n<br />\nCall車要講明比幾份禮物(貼士)先肯黎<br />\n<br />\n不過是撚但啦，成個澳門都係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfc0594c89daf15edea89758cfb8a5e1404e1bf","tid":669304,"uid":127569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"傻既先去澳門，正常人根本唔會去呢d鬼地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f58f0848a5f3d889561dc2fd2ad848f32113cd3","tid":669304,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9960ef8609786a442e6fe71b834323d6391e1b97","tid":669304,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"帶定架生去啦,有咩事可以威嚇司機或者打爆車窗逃生"},{"pid":"a9f5f5cbff3330112bb946cc4e471644359ee645","tid":669304,"uid":176442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:29:15.000Z","msg":"澳門亂象，衰過清朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550f3fc1d8eded982a59da46692a261ae8a25f68","tid":669304,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"澳門除左賭錢同叫雞之外就無存在意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}